process.kill();


Instance de eventEmitter 

event `exist `
event `uncaughtExeption`


 ***Interacting with File system 
 
 Wrappers around POSIX functions ( async and sync versions) 
 
 ex: fs.readdir(path, callback) and fs.readdirSync(path);
 
 Stream Oriented functions 
 
fs.createReadStream() -- return a fs.readStream Readable Stream 
fs.CreateWriteStream() - returns an fs.writeStream Writable stream

WE can also watch a directory or file for changes ( if file changes or directory) 
 